### Notes:
Stage 4 - Performing
This is the stage when the team is on its way to success.
In the performing stage, members are motivated and familiar enough with the project and their team that they can operate confidently and independently.
Everyone is on the same page and driving full-speed ahead towards the final goal.
The fourth stage is the one that all groups strive to reach.
Yet, those that fail to overcome conflicts and can’t work together do not make it here.
Strategy
Motivate each other to be productive and celebrate small successes.
Monitor your own progress and develop more productive habits, especially if you are working remotely.
Seek help and clarification early. Offer help where you can afford.
